A Special Birthday Celebration
</h2>

<h1 class="title">

Happy Birthday

<span>My Princess</span>

</h1>

<img src="photo.jpg" class="photo">

<h3 class="name">
Charishma ❤️
</h3>

<p class="message">

Every smile of yours is priceless.

May your life always be filled with happiness,

good health,

