Beautiful Memories

</h2>

<div class="images">

<img src="photo.jpg">

<img src="photo.jpg">

<img src="photo.jpg">

</div>

</section>

<section class="letter">

<h2>

A Letter From

Jashwanth ❤️

</h2>

<p>

Dear Charishma,

You are one of the most precious blessings in my life.

I always wish to see you smiling because your happiness means a lot to me.

May this birthday bring unlimited joy,

success,

peace,

love,

and wonderful opportunities into your life.

May all your dreams come true.

Stay happy forever.

Happy Birthday My Princess.

With lots of love,

Jashwanth ❤️

</p>

</section>

<section class="surprise">

<button id="surpriseBtn">

🎁 Click For Surprise

</button>

